{"tid":2191321,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如果一定要搞街頭遊行，現階段起碼要「民陣」肯落水先得。","createTime":"2020-09-06T11:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T11:40:11.000Z","uid":219007,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"61c89c408d5dd3fdf5c2f26737023597519a51ba","tid":2191321,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T11:11:04.000Z","msg":"利申：我反對而家任何街頭抗爭，因為現階段應該係盡量減少自己付出既代價。<br />\n<br />\n退後一步咁講，就當真係好想遊行。 面對而家靜咗咁耐，要搞得返起個勢，第一步最起碼係要民陣肯吹雞先。 始終佢號召力最大，一日佢唔撚吹雞，靜左咁耐冇民陣一定冇人睬你地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c82bc9b48502a25fb9b224707c0fcd70f208dec","tid":2191321,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T11:13:46.000Z","msg":"補充<br />\n<br />\n一係你哋就日日喺民陣fb 洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係佢睬你嘅機會都應該好細，因為民陴基本上搞唔到非法遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9c65dbff2c14f7cdbf1352c7fdaa3482c558a9","tid":2191321,"uid":273703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T11:15:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0dc6f8386c1fe9dccfad976ad57d8b536174179e","tid":2191321,"uid":273703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T11:17:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b2c0318a89e767b4d20193d62e84409d6ccc39b","tid":2191321,"uid":145423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T11:18:26.000Z","msg